title: MOJA Festival’s ‘Stick Fly’ performances Friday and Saturday canceled
text: MOJA Festival’s ‘Stick Fly’ performances Friday and Saturday canceled Oct 2 2015 4:01 pm Oct 2 4:03 pm Performances on Friday and Saturday of Art Forms and Theatre Concepts’ show “Stick Fly,” presented as part of the MOJA Arts Festival, have been cancelled due to bad weather. All tickets will be honored at Sunday’s performance, scheduled for 6 p.m. Sunday at the Dock Street Theatre, 135 Church St. Staff report
